{
  "id": "69f7c484d6cc78c4025f12be",
  "title": "2026/03/29―Summer498",
  "created": 1777845381,
  "updated": 1777845387,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69f7c484d6cc78c4025f12be",
      "text": "2026/03/29―Summer498",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777845381,
      "updated": 1777845381
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c4850000000000bd5c4d",
      "text": "from [2026/03/29]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777845381,
      "updated": 1777845381
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c4850000000000bd5c4e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777845381,
      "updated": 1777845383
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c4850000000000bd5c4f",
      "text": "[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777845381,
      "updated": 1777845381
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c4850000000000bd5c50",
      "text": "\t縦書きのページを作りたかった",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777845381,
      "updated": 1777845381
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c4850000000000bd5c51",
      "text": "\tやり方を間違えるとUIが全崩壊するので試すなら個人ページ上のCSSで。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777845381,
      "updated": 1777845381
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c4850000000000bd5c52",
      "text": "\t\tやらかしてもページの名前を書き換えて一時的に個人ページがないことにして復旧できる。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777845381,
      "updated": 1777845381
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c4850000000000bd5c53",
      "text": "\t文字列を縦書きにするのは簡単なのだが、画像の埋め込み位置などの行組を変える必要がある。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777845381,
      "updated": 1777845381
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c4850000000000bd5c54",
      "text": "\tスクロールが下にしか行かないのが問題なのかも",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777845381,
      "updated": 1777845381
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c4850000000000bd5c55",
      "text": "\tテロメアがマーカーのように伸びてくる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777845381,
      "updated": 1777845381
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c4850000000000bd5c56",
      "text": "\t全てが横書き前提で設計されているのが分かって面白い",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777845381,
      "updated": 1777845381
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c4850000000000bd5c57",
      "text": "\t素朴な発想であれば、画面を右に90度回転させて、文字のみ回転を解除するイメージなんだけど、",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777845381,
      "updated": 1777845381
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c4850000000000bd5c58",
      "text": "\t\t実際は画面を右に90度回転が難しい。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777845381,
      "updated": 1777845381
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c4850000000000bd5c59",
      "text": "\t\t回転させられるとは夢にも思っていまい",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777845381,
      "updated": 1777845381
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c4850000000000bd5c5a",
      "text": "\tカスペックPCだけどVRCワールド作りたいと少し思ってしまった",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777845381,
      "updated": 1777845381
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c4850000000000bd5c5b",
      "text": "\t[Chat GPT の話し方]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777845381,
      "updated": 1777845381
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c4850000000000bd5c5c",
      "text": "\t円・銭・厘の頃の金銭感覚",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777845381,
      "updated": 1777845381
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c4850000000000bd5c5d",
      "text": "\t\t大雑把に旧1円＝現1万円くらいに思って考えると",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777845381,
      "updated": 1777845381
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c4850000000000bd5c5e",
      "text": "\t\t旧1円 = 100銭 = 1'000厘",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777845381,
      "updated": 1777845381
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c4850000000000bd5c5f",
      "text": "\t\t旧1円 = 10'000円",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777845381,
      "updated": 1777845381
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c4850000000000bd5c60",
      "text": "\t\t旧1銭 = 100円",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777845381,
      "updated": 1777845381
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c4850000000000bd5c61",
      "text": "\t\t旧1厘 = 10円",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777845381,
      "updated": 1777845381
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c4850000000000bd5c62",
      "text": "\t両・文の頃の金銭感覚",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777845381,
      "updated": 1777845381
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c4850000000000bd5c63",
      "text": "\t\t大雑把に旧1両＝現1万円くらいに思って考えると",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777845381,
      "updated": 1777845381
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c4850000000000bd5c64",
      "text": "\t\t1両 = 4'000文",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777845381,
      "updated": 1777845381
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c4850000000000bd5c65",
      "text": "\t\t1両 = 10'000 円",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777845381,
      "updated": 1777845381
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c4850000000000bd5c66",
      "text": "\t\t1文 = 2.5 円",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777845381,
      "updated": 1777845381
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c4850000000000bd5c67",
      "text": "\t区切り方が現代の金銭感覚に通じるものがある。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777845381,
      "updated": 1777845381
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c4850000000000bd5c68",
      "text": "\t\t万円単位で考えたり、100円単位で考えたり、10円単位で考えることは多い",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777845381,
      "updated": 1777845381
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c4850000000000bd5c69",
      "text": "\t若くて成熟していて老齢の人が寿命で死ぬ瞬間に言いそうなこと",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777845381,
      "updated": 1777845381
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c4850000000000bd5c6a",
      "text": "\t\t「明日〇〇の予定やったけどお迎え来そうなのでキャンセルします。追伸：2日後くらいに式があると思うので、予定を開けておいてくれると家族が助かります。」",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777845381,
      "updated": 1777845381
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c4850000000000bd5c6b",
      "text": " \t\tみたいなノリ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777845381,
      "updated": 1777845381
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c4850000000000bd5c6c",
      "text": " \t達観しすぎていて聖人になりそう",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777845381,
      "updated": 1777845381
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c4850000000000bd5c6d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777845381,
      "updated": 1777845381
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c48a0000000000bd5c6e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777845386,
      "updated": 1777845386
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7c48a0000000000bd5c6f",
      "text": "[2026/05/04 お試し個別日記を作成]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
